title: Aer Lingus Passenger Flips Out, Bites Fellow Passenger, Dies
text:
Aer Lingus Passenger Flips Out, Bites Fellow Passenger, Dies 
Published By: Gawker.com - Today 
A 24-year-old man became agitated on an Aer Lingus flight from Lisbon to Dublin, bit another man, fell unconscious, and later died, reports ...
